Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:58.32,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:04.58,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:09.88,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:16.39,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:23.02,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:29.36,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:38.07,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:44.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:51.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.34,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:03.22,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,And rise back up again and again and again
